        <div>
            <label>ุชูููุช ุงูููู ุงูุฃูู (ุณุงุนุงุชุ ุฏูุงุฆูุ ุซูุงูู):</label>
            <input type="number" id="day1Hours" placeholder="ุณุงุนุงุช">
            <input type="number" id="day1Minutes" placeholder="ุฏูุงุฆู">
            <input type="number" id="day1Seconds" placeholder="ุซูุงูู">
        </div>
        <div>
            <label>ุชูููุช ุงูููู ุงูุซุงูู (ุณุงุนุงุชุ ุฏูุงุฆูุ ุซูุงูู):</label>
            <input type="number" id="day2Hours" placeholder="ุณุงุนุงุช">
